Headhunter
The Headhunter is a professional mercenary soldier: skilled, heavily armed,
and for hire to anyone who can afford the rate. They are among the best
non-Coalition soldiers on Rifts Earth.

Headhunters begin with a strong military skill base including demolitions,
two vehicle specialisations, and multiple weapon proficiencies. They choose
from Espionage, Military, Physical, Pilot, Technical, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: PS 10, PE 10.
Starting equipment: Body armour, two modern ranged weapons, one melee weapon,
combat knife, radio communicator, and mercenary ID papers.
